Package models

Class User

java.lang.Object
models.User
Direct Known Subclasses:
Staff, Student
public class User extends Object
The User class represents a user in CAMs. Users have a unique ID, password, name, and faculty. Each user also has a Role which determines their level of access.

This class provides a basic structure for user-related functionalities within the CAMs system.

Since:
1.0
Version:

Author:
